          <p class="disclaimer"><em>This article is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal or tax advice. CCA rules, capital gains treatment, and the section 45 elections depend on your specific circumstances. Always consult a qualified CPA or tax professional before making tax decisions. Regulations change frequently. Verify current rules with the CRA.</em></p>

